    %h2 About Us
    %p Portland Code School students learn from experienced programmers, develop the skills needed to join a leading tech company, and have direct access to local sponsoring companies interested in hiring new developers.
    %p There is a huge and rapidly growing demand for able-minded programmers who are not only capable of skillful programming, but also skillful at communicating with clients and peers. Tech shops cannot exist with single-faceted programmers alone; the most valuable programmers are those that easily interact with clients and produce outstanding quality code.

  .tan
    %section.width
      %h2 Our Mission
      %p To teach passionate, smart, creative people the skills they need to be competent, well-rounded programmers, able to excel in a web development career and to provide ongoing professional development opportunities to all programmers.

  %section.width
    %h2 Our Vision
    %p We believe in Portland, its heart, energy, enthusiasm, kindness, and sincerity, and we believe that Portland is going to be the center of an artistic digital revolution and a hub for all the creative passionate artists in the world why ply their trade on the digital canvas. As the leader in web development education in Portland, we provide a way for people to realize their dreams and pay their rent.

    We believe there is a space for small companies and wild hares. We support their efforts by building relationships between companies and communities and by training developers that are capable of realizing their employer's visions and adding their own to the canvas.

    We believe in the power of community to bring people together and make anything possible.We create communities that are welcoming to everyone including women, low income individuals, and those that are often at a disadvantage in technology. We create communities that hum with energy and passion.

    We believe the education system has failed to educate the public about web development. We are a world class model for teaching the latest, cutting edge web development technologies; it is through our partnerships that we transform the way web development is taught and how employers support and educate new developers.

    We believe Portland is an oasis for tech companies and one of the best places to work in the world. Like Portland, we are an oasis for learning web development and we are the best code school. 
